org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.exec.persistence

Class MapJoinBytesTableContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.exec.persistence.MapJoinBytesTableContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MemoryEstimate, MapJoinTableContainer, MapJoinTableContainerDirectAccess

    public class MapJoinBytesTableContainer
extends Object
implements MapJoinTableContainer, MapJoinTableContainerDirectAccess
    Table container that serializes keys and values using LazyBinarySerDe into BytesBytesMultiHashMap, with very low memory overhead. However, there may be some perf overhead when retrieving rows.
